snippet.title: Asym Altered Axis Pre-Alpha Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Asym Altered Axis is a Cross-genre Asymmetric Multiplayer Game (1vs5) between 1 Real-time Strategy players versus up to 5 Co-op Stealth Action players!

The Alpha Test will be available soon on Steam!

Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1845210


For updates and news on Asym Altered Axis, follow us on social media!

Discord: https://discord.gg/EC8cteB9u8
Twitter: https://twitter.com/AsymAlteredAxis
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/AsymAlteredAxis/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/asymalteredaxis/
Tik Tok: https://www.tiktok.com/@asymalteredaxis
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/AsymAlteredAxis/

*Work in progress - Pre-Alpha footage
